                                    ></path><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"
                                    ></circle></svg
                                >
                            </div>
                            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">
                                Who I Am
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="space-y-4 text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8 relative z-10"
                        >
                            <p>
                                I am a Full-stack developer experienced in
                                creating modern and efficient web applications
                                using JavaScript, React, and Astro.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                I focus on development best practices,
                                performance, and solid user experience in both
                                frontend and backend.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                I have knowledge in cybersecurity applied to
                                system and application protection, integrating
                                security principles from design to
                                implementation.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Additionally, I develop projects in data science
                                and artificial intelligence, with an emphasis on
                                predictive models and prompt engineering,
                                integrating these areas to build complete,
                                secure, and innovative technological solutions.
                            </p>
                        </div>
